import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'
import City from '../../Components/Area/City'
import Banner from '../../Components/Banner/Banner'
import CardBanner from '../../Components/Banner/CardBanner'

import HomeBanner from '../../Components/Banner/HomeBanner'

import PropertyListing from '../../Components/Listing/PropertyListing'
import FeaturedProjects from '../../Components/Projects/FeaturedProjects'
import TrendingProjects from '../../Components/Projects/TrandingProjects'


const Home = () => {
  return (
    
    <Box>
     
     <Banner />
     <CardBanner />
     
     <Box p={3} mt={2}>

      
   
       
     
          
       {/* recently add */}
       <PropertyListing />   
       <HomeBanner />  

       {/* project section  */}
       <FeaturedProjects />
       <TrendingProjects />
       <HomeBanner /> 
       <City />

     </Box>
    
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Home
